sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (Browser)
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant S3 as MinIO
    participant DB as MySQL

    U->>API: POST /api/posts (multipart form + JWT cookie)
    API->>API: get_current_user (JWT decode)
    API->>API: validate text length / MIME / size
    API->>S3: upload_file(key, bytes) for each image
    S3-->>API: 200 OK
    API->>DB: transaction - INSERT posts then INSERT images
    API->>DB: SELECT post + user + images
    API-->>U: 200 PostResponse (+presigned image URLs)
